text:
@marcorubio Of all the people in the world I want to hear from regarding the #coronavirus, Marco Rubio is at the bottom of the list.
The #GOP has allowed the Trump administration to weaken whatever emergency procedures that had been in place prior to 2017.  This one will be on the #GOP.
